snippet.title: Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel - Claptastic Voyage Trailer
snippet.description:
Claptastic Voyage and Ultimate Vault Hunter Upgrade Pack 2 is the fourth add-on content pack from Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel and will be available on March 24.
